.TH "LIGHTNING-LIQUIDITY-REPORT" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-liquidity-report \- summarise total Lightning liquidity
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning liquidity-report
.SH DESCRIPTION
Aggregates local and remote satoshis across all channels and reports
liquidity health.
A channel is
.I balanced
when the local ratio is 20%\(en80%;
.I depleted
when local ratio is below 10%.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"total_local_sat":N,"total_remote_sat":N,"total_capacity_sat":N,
 "local_ratio":F,"num_channels":N,
 "balanced_channels":N,"depleted_channels":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-balance (1),
.BR lightning-node-health (1)
